'''Uzziel Ndagijimana''' ni umuhanga mu bukungu w’u Rwanda wabaye Minisitiri w’imari n’igenamigambi muri guverinoma ya [[Perezida wa Repubulika y’u Rwanda|Perezida]] [[Paul Kagame]] kuva mu 2018. <ref name=":0">https://mobile-reuters-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKBN1HE08H?amp_js_v=a2&amp_gsa=1&usqp=mq331AQCCAE=#referrer=https://www.google.com&amp_tf=From%20%251$s&ampshare=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-rwanda-economy/rwandas-president-names-new-finance-minister-in-reshuffle-idUSKBN1HE08H</ref> <ref name=":1">http://www.minecofin.gov.rw/index.php?id=12&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=665&cHash=037640c4bf62c4aca3044121e01d7128</ref>

== Ubuzima bwambere nuburere ==
Ndagijimana afite impamyabumenyi ya PhD m'ubukungu, yabonye muri 1998 yakuye mu Ishuri ryUbukungu rya Warsaw . <ref>https://www.theigc.org/person/uzziel-ngagijimana/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ndagijimana yatangiye umwuga we wo kuba umwarimu mu ishami ry’ubukungu, ubumenyi bw’imibereho n’imiyoborere muri [[kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda]] mu 1999. Mu 2002, yimukiye mu myanya y'ubuyobozi ya Guverinoma y'u Rwanda. <ref name=":2">https://live.worldbank.org/experts/uzziel-ndagijimana</ref> Ndagijimana yabaye umuyobozi w’ishuri ry’imari n’amabanki i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]], kuva 2002 kugeza 2007 nyuma yaje kuba umuyobozi wungirije wa kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda kuva 2007 kugeza 2011. <ref name=":2" /> <ref name=":3">https://www.theigc.org/person/uzziel-ngagijimana/</ref> Ndagijimana yari umunyamabanga uhoraho wa Minisiteri y’ubuzima, Repubulika y’u Rwanda kuva muri Gicurasi 2011 kugeza Nyakanga 2014.  Yabaye kandi Umunyamabanga wa Leta ushinzwe igenamigambi ry’Ubukungu muri Minisiteri y’Imari n’Igenamigambi (MINECOFIN). Mu nama rusange ngarukamwaka ya Afreximbank i [[Abuja]] yo kwizihiza isabukuru yimyaka 25, Kemi Adeosun, minisitiri w’imari wa Nijeriya, yasimbuye Ndagijimana nk'umuyobozi w’inama y’amabanki. <ref>https://www.today.ng/business/finance/kemi-adeosun-elected-afreximbank-board-chairperson-132840</ref> Ku ya 7 Mata 2018, Ndagijimana yagizwe Minisitiri w’imari n’igenamigambi mu Rwanda na Perezida [[Paul Kagame]] .  Ndagijimana kandi yabaye Umuyobozi w'Inama Ngishwanama ku bukungu ya Perezida wa Repubulika y'u Rwanda. 

